iew/README.md:\n  Line 41: It does not investigate outward knowledge (`deep-research`), map inward code before planning (`deep-context`), compare competing plans (`deep-ai-council`) or run evaluator-first improvement lanes (`deep-improvement`). A single-pass review is `sk-code-review`. The five top-level deep-loop personas share the `deep-loop-runtime` for executors, state handling and coverage graphs.\n\n  Line 114: Skip it for a single-pass review, where `sk-code-review` is faster. Skip it for external investigation (`deep-research`), inward code mapping (`deep-context`) or strategy comparison (`deep-ai-council`).\n\n\n(Results truncated. Consider using a more specific path or pattern.)","metadata":{"matches":100,"truncated":true},"title":"ai-council|mode: all|mode: subagent|--agent ai-council|\\.opencode/agents/.*toml|runtime mirrors|deep-route-guard|mk-deep-loop-guard|orchestrate|Deep Route","time":{"start":1782919293161,"end":1782919293191}},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"fc_0963fe6f9a3705f5016a45307aa7108191b90eb8e7ce7ad353"}},"id":"prt_f1e45682a0014lh527WVAa0UHT","sessionID":"ses_0e1c04adcffe04QJWsDQQqIgY4","messageID":"msg_f1e44d1b6001f5VP642WE3exff"}}
